    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear that, but it seems like both sides of the aisle say the same thing about the other side. like the left says the right uses fake news to spread lies, and the right says the left uses media bias to hide the truth. so if everyone is calling everyone else liars, isn't \"fake news\" just a subjective tool used for delegitimizing opponents?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
